November 12, 1968. No. 132,

October Term, 1965.

Holt et al. v. Kirby et al., Robert L. Bobrick on the motion. John E. Tobin and Benjamin Vinar for Kirby et al., and Mark F. Hughes and Vincent R. Fitzpatrick for Alleghany Corp., in opposition.

384 U. S. 28, 967. Motion of Morris Smith et al. to recall and amend judgment in this case denied.

Mr. Justice Fortas and Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
